Last Updated: 01/04/2024

# 1. Information Collection and Use
Me, Sébastien, developer of Pixxel, are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect and how it is used.
- User Provided Information: Pixxel may collect user-provided information such as Discord usernames, IDs, and server information necessary for the functionality of the bot's features. This information is solely used for the intended purposes of the bot's mini-games, utility features, and other functionalities.
- Usage Data: We may collect data on how users interact with the bot, including game scores, command usage, and other usage patterns. This data is used for analytics and to improve and optimize the bot's performance. It helps us understand user preferences and enhance the overall user experience.

# 2. Data Storage and Security
- Data Storage: User data collected by Pixxel is stored securely on our servers. We take measures to ensure the confidentiality and integrity of this data. We do not sell or share user information with third parties, except as required by law.
- Security: We implement reasonable security measures to protect user data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction. These measures include encryption, access controls, and regular security audits to mitigate potential risks.

# 3. Third-Party Services
- Discord API: Pixxel interacts with the Discord API to provide its services. Users are subject to Discord's Terms of Service and Privacy Policy. We do not have control over Discord's data handling practices, and users are encouraged to review Discord's policies independently.

# 4. Cookies
Pixxel does not use cookies for tracking purposes. The bot does not store any information on users' devices. All data is processed and stored on our secure servers.

# 5. Children’s Privacy
Pixxel is not intended for users under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from children. If you believe that we might have any information from or about a child under 13, please contact us. We will promptly take steps to delete such information.

# 6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
Sébastien reserves the right to update this Privacy Policy. Users will be notified of any changes through Discord or other communication channels. Continued use of Pixxel implies acceptance of the updated policy.

# 7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at https://discord.com/invite/7NBBbNmavv. We are committed to addressing inquiries and ensuring a transparent and secure user experience.

By using Pixxel, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
